{"tid":784050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一貼傳銷狗樣","createTime":"2018-08-18T05:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T09:53:28.000Z","uid":175752,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b472ec21e782fd2f1aa05fe78ce79ebb2e97046c","tid":784050,"uid":175752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"旺角傳銷狗<br />\n（專sell美容/教育etc)<br />\n所有交友apps都見到佢呃人<br />\n聲稱自己個名叫「污糟」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樣似坤狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聲稱讀UST<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇比佢呃過，係垃圾傳銷朋友嘅同事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/130929_2c175233d4b9b2a784cbf49d5d29c396.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F130929_2c175233d4b9b2a784cbf49d5d29c396.png&h=dc50bb50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"747474df5606b05002cfeb08ab46b49ee9358f50","tid":784050,"uid":175752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傳銷狗死全家"},{"pid":"c68e5042f6d0ec1358876038f872c0f4dcf0f74b","tid":784050,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07b646585460beebad05dacb76637ef688b23be","tid":784050,"uid":169096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/133348_5873ff1a76832d2b21fa40b179e848de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F133348_5873ff1a76832d2b21fa40b179e848de.png&h=8fa81fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/133350_8fbeafb64b435161f3fab38a64acbff7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F133350_8fbeafb64b435161f3fab38a64acbff7.png&h=157e7565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間公司叫Francine，前身為亮碧思<br />\n係旺角東果邊，亞皆老街怡安閣<br />\n個大堂裝修得勁靚 好似酒店大堂咁<br />\n條友自稱堂哥<br />\n正職x藝體育會游水教練，堅尼地城負責人<br />\n專呃人做生意，賣紅酒 保健產品 珠寶 奶粉<br />\n會叫你加盟，夾錢，話之後會揾到好多錢<br />\n朋友仲係學生，入世未深，就咁比佢呃左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n揾左其他資料，有其他巴打中伏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/558994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/558994</a>"},{"pid":"561059b2908f6b9059d3671d90ffd3482176395d","tid":784050,"uid":175752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傳銷狗死全家"},{"pid":"47a05a574b5e445914b32e06a47c2c475647eee2","tid":784050,"uid":67230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"杰哥"},{"pid":"3ed6ff6aa34b012e223fcfa6098bea6f80feeb9e","tid":784050,"uid":135313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"高汁post<br />\n話佢地傳銷狗根本侮辱緊啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc4738980e57ad8b29b0723838a3536e8799d90","tid":784050,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"推一推，比多啲人知，唔好有人再中伏"},{"pid":"af94a44c35b659b15fcbade2e7a21501d40b89ca","tid":784050,"uid":175752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1e2666017a49e26c666f209ed95614f88561a4","tid":784050,"uid":169096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"近排又多返傳銷撚樣出嚟呃人"},{"pid"